dataList.name: Qraved - Best Food Restaurant Dining Finder

dataList.appIntro:
Qraved is the No.1 Food and Restaurant Directory App in Indonesia. It is the best way to search and discover food around you. Browse through the latest trending Qraved journal, Instagram foodie photos, reviews, recipes, food delivery and make reservations online.
Whether you’re looking for a McDonald’s or KFC that just opened, or a Starbucks nearby, Qraved will guide you to the perfect place to dine-out. Qraved analyzes your activity and foody preferences to give you the best restaurant suggestions. 
Treat yourself to a nice restaurant and share the experience with your friends on social media. Save the restaurants you like and log your food journey with reviews and tasty photos. 
**Features**
Find Restaurants:
•  Find the best restaurants, bars and hotels to dine in the area
•  Make reservations online
•  Filter restaurant search by cuisine (e.g. Italian, Indonesian, Japanese, Halal), location/  landmark (e.g. Senayan, Thamrin, Grand Indonesia, Kota Kasablanka, PIK), name (e.g. Domino’s Pizza, McDelivery, Ayam Goreng KFC, Hokben, Genki Sushi, Flip Burger) and more
•  Find great promotions and discounts offered by local restaurants
Search Restaurants Nearest to you:
•  Discover nearby restaurants
•  Watch videos, read food journals, recipes and reviews by Qraved community before deciding where to eat
•  View menu, addresses, Instagram photos, phone numbers to call or make a booking online directly from the app
•  Use the map view to explore restaurants around you and click pins to specific areas
Share and Write Reviews:
•  Write and read reviews, upload photos and share it to friends on social media (e.g. Facebook, Twitter, Email, LINE, WhatsApp)
•  Share your food journey with reviews and amazing photos, all will be logged in your food journey
Other Features:
•  Find and save restaurant ideas by creating your own Qraved list
•  Read the latest trending food journals/articles and videos
•  Edit your food and brand preferences for curated results
Find the best restaurants, read expert reviews and start looking for restaurants near you with Qraved. The difference between Qraved and other food discovery apps (e.g. Gojek, Gofood, Zomato, Tripadvisor, Foursquare, Yelp, Cookpad) is that it focuses on connecting people to food to life, and having an open network to integrate various social contents.
 
Qraved is now available 6 major cities in Indonesia including Jakarta, Bali, Bandung, Surabaya, Medan and Makassar. More locations are coming very soon. Yuk makan dan juga lihat resep kuliner enak dan murah, download Qraved Now!
